Package: OECDHousingToolkit
Type: Package
Title: Provide Rmarkdown template to generate chapters of the OECD housing toolkit and OECD Housing horizontal project country fiches
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Manuel Betin, Federica Depace, Maxime Nguyen
Maintainer: The package maintainer <manuel.betin@oecd.org>
Description: contains all the functions and templates to generate uniform figures,data manipulation and html documents necessary to populate the housing toolkit. The package also includes a template to generate country fiches
